AmbiSecure helps organizations accelerate to a password-less future by providing support for the FIDO2 protocol. FIDO2 supports not only today’s Two Factor authentication but also paves the way for eliminating weak password authentication with strong single-factor hardware-based authentication. 

The AmbiSecure provides a simple and intuitive authentication experience that users find easy to use, ensuring rapid adoption and organizational #security. 

